text: Theodore Tartakover (11 May 1887 - 28 November 1977) was an Australian swimmer. He competed at the 1908 Summer Olympics and the 1912 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1887 births Category:1977 deaths Category:Australian male swimmers Category:Olympic swimmers of Australasia Category:Swimmers at the 1908 Summer Olympics Category:Swimmers at the 1912 Summer Olympics
